如果我们在下个交通灯那里右转
就会经过

682
00:36:51,640 --> 00:36:54,060
* It doesn't matter what they say *

683
00:36:54,060 --> 00:36:59,290
* in the jealous games people play, hey ey ey *

684
00:37:25,330 --> 00:37:26,130
没有看见他

685
